      "source_region": "div#content",
      "text": "Let $k\\geq 2$ and $n$ be sufficiently large depending on $k$. Let $A=\\{a_1<a_2<\\cdots \\}$ be the set of those integers in $[n,n^k]$ which have a divisor in $(n,2n)$. Estimate\\[\\max_{i} a_{i+1}-a_i.\\]Is this $\\leq (\\log n)^{O(1)}$?"
    }
